data.description: Located on a dead street in the desirable quiet neighborhood of Oak Shore Heights. This home backs up to legacy trail to ride bikes and park. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home has been completely updated. All appliances and air conditioner within 2 years. Security system, all new flooring, new garage door and opener. Pinecraft area, this home also gives opportunity for the perfect investment property.  Spacious wooded lot with oak trees. This is truly a must see.
